data.description: Live close to where you play! Well maintained Doublewide Manufactured home sits surrounded by Ponderosa Pines on a generously sized 1.24 acre corner lot. The property has plenty of storage for all your toys with three outbuildings; RV garage with additional storage space, Storage Shed, and one car garage. The home is 3 bedroom, 2 bath with an additional den/TV room. The home is on a block foundation with a metal roof. The kitchen and bathrooms have newer floors. A fenced in dog area in the front of the home with access gates provides safety for your animals. HOA maintains roads and snow removal.
